citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 10:40 am on 28-
SEPT-2023. The licensee stated there were two appointments arriving in the next hour or so that could not be changed,
and since there were no other employees present, there was no one who could accompany the inspection.
End Section
